## Architecture

```
AI agent / Claude Code
    │
    └─ rules-mcp (stdio MCP server)
           │
           ├─ Registry (in-memory register.jsonl index)
           │  ├─ search() — token-based scoring
           │  ├─ list_files() — category filtering
           │  └─ learning_path() — layer grouping
           │
           └─ Adapter (7 MCP tools)
              ├─ help
              ├─ search_rules
              ├─ get_rule
              ├─ get_context
              ├─ get_learning_path
              ├─ list_rules
              └─ get_related
```

## Tools (7 total)

| Tool | Layer | Purpose |
|------|-------|---------|
| `help` | adapter | Overview + categories + quick start |
| `search_rules(query, category?, limit?)` | adapter | Token-based weighted search |
| `get_rule(file)` | adapter | Read markdown from Rules repo |
| `get_context(languages, topics?)` | adapter | All rules for languages |
| `get_learning_path(languages, phase?)` | adapter | Phased reading order by layer |
| `list_rules(category?)` | adapter | Category-filtered listing |
| `get_related(file)` | adapter | Follow edge graph (requires/feeds/related) |

